tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE biometric_data (
    id INT NOT NULL,
    user_id INT NOT NULL,
    fingerprint_data BYTEA,
    scan_timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    PRIMARY KEY (id),
    FOREIGN KEY (user_id) REFERENCES users(id)
);

CREATE TABLE biometric_user (
  user_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  fingerprint_scan BYTEA
)

CREATE TABLE biometric_admin (
  admin_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  fingerprint_scan BYTEA
)

CREATE TABLE biometric_log (
  log_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  user_id INT,
  admin_id INT,
  access_time TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE biometric_history (
  user_id INT,
  action VARCHAR,
  timestamp TIMESTAMP
)
